{"tid":868016,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓朝即將解除共同警備區武裝　民眾遊客可自由出入","createTime":"2018-10-19T06:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T07:21:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"44a8b13e5c271ef1d206a815e2caef11266881c1","tid":868016,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181019/s00005/6dbc9386b6e89823b955469ae7425543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181019%2Fs00005%2F6dbc9386b6e89823b955469ae7425543.jpg&h=726dc6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓朝防長上月簽署軍事協議，承諾撤出板門店共同警備區（Joint Security Area，JSA）內的武力，讓韓朝民眾和外國遊客可自由跨越軍事分界線進出JSA。<br />\n<br />\n為解除JSA的武裝，韓朝雙方從本月1日起在JSA掃雷。韓聯社引述韓國政府消息人士透露，韓方已完成掃雷，朝方也進入結尾階段，明日將完成工作。朝方至今發現5枚地雷並已引爆，韓方則沒有找到地雷。<br />\n<br />\n據韓朝軍事協議規定，雙方需在完成掃雷後5天內，撤出兵力和武器，朝方將撤走5個哨所，韓方將撤走4個哨所，JSA內的衝鋒槍、AK-47步槍、手槍等武器均全部撤出。<br />\n<br />\n解除武裝後，韓朝將各派35人在JSA內執勤，執勤人員佩戴黃底藍色的「板門店民事警察」袖章，並不攜帶槍械。韓朝民眾和外國遊客可於上午9時到下午5時自由出入JSA。<br />\n<br />\n(韓聯社)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181019/s00005/1539920968638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181019%2Fs00005%2F1539920968638&d=Vm5jeO38HcOihhMeOd%2BulvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=bcb48249\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181019%2Fs00005%2F1539920968638&h=b7309124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181019/s00005/1539920968638</a>"},{"pid":"34c8b2b91774c5acde188489d3e33c31929d7ff0","tid":868016,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t6h4ZdQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft6h4ZdQ.gif&h=e8eb2c25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"062c074a1de64c